@startuml level-3b-components-supervision
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml
HIDE_STEREOTYPE()

title JOTP Level 3: Supervision Components

Container_Boundary(super, "Supervision System") {

  Component(supervisor, "Supervisor", "Supervision Tree", "Restart strategies (sealed)\nChildren lifecycle mgmt\nSliding restart window\nDynamic child addition")

  Component(strategies, "RestartStrategy", "Strategy Enum", "ONE_FOR_ONE (isolated)\nONE_FOR_ALL (cascade)\nREST_FOR_ONE (ordered)\nSIMPLE_ONE_FOR_ONE (pool)")

  Component(childspec, "ChildSpec<S,M>", "Child Specification", "RestartType sealed:\nPERMANENT/TRANSIENT/TEMPORARY\nShutdown sealed: BrutalKill/Timeout\nChildType: WORKER/SUPERVISOR")

  Component(autoshutdown, "AutoShutdown", "Supervisor Lifecycle", "NEVER: ignore child exit\nANY_SIGNIFICANT: one PERMANENT exit\nALL_SIGNIFICANT: all PERMANENT exit\nControls supervisor termination")

  Component(crashrecovery, "CrashRecovery", "Retry on Crash", "Isolated virtual thread retries\nExponential backoff support\nDead letter queue fallback\nLet-it-crash recovery pattern")

  Component(appcontroller, "ApplicationController", "App Lifecycle", "Top-level supervisor\nStart/stop orchestration\nBoot sequence management\nGraceful shutdown coordination")

  Component(appspec, "ApplicationSpec", "App Configuration", "Initial supervisor tree\nBoot timeout\nInitialization function\nApplication state holder")

  Component(appcallback, "ApplicationCallback", "App Hooks", "onReady callback\nonShutdown callback\nonError handler\nHealthcheck endpoint")

  Component(starttype, "StartType", "Child Start Enum", "Sealed enum\nIMMEDIATE: spawn now\nDELAYED: spawn later\nDEPENDENT: after parents")

  Component(runtype, "RunType", "Child Run Mode", "Sealed enum\nFOREGROUND: normal\nBACKGROUND: detached\nBOOT_ONLY: startup phase")

  Rel(supervisor, childspec, "manages via")
  Rel(supervisor, strategies, "uses restart")
  Rel(supervisor, crashrecovery, "applies on crash")
  Rel(childspec, autoshutdown, "controls via")
  Rel(childspec, starttype, "defines start")
  Rel(childspec, runtype, "defines run mode")
  Rel(appcontroller, supervisor, "creates root")
  Rel(appcontroller, appspec, "configures with")
  Rel(appcontroller, appcallback, "invokes hooks")

  note right of supervisor
    **Supervisor** — OTP supervision tree:
    Manages children lifecycle (start, stop, restart).
    Restart window: sliding N failures in M seconds.
    Dynamic child management: startChild/terminateChild/deleteChild.
    Nested hierarchies support.
  end note

  note right of strategies
    **RestartStrategy** — Sealed enum:
    ONE_FOR_ONE: restart only failed child (isolated).
    ONE_FOR_ALL: restart all children (cascade failure).
    REST_FOR_ONE: restart failed + all started after (ordered).
    SIMPLE_ONE_FOR_ONE: dynamic homogeneous pools.
  end note

  note right of childspec
    **ChildSpec<S,M>** — Child configuration:
    RestartType sealed: PERMANENT/TRANSIENT/TEMPORARY.
    Shutdown sealed: BrutalKill/Timeout(secs)/Infinity.
    ChildType: WORKER/SUPERVISOR.
    Start timeout, args, id.
  end note

  note right of autoshutdown
    **AutoShutdown** — Supervisor lifecycle:
    NEVER: supervisor ignores all child exits.
    ANY_SIGNIFICANT: exit if any PERMANENT child dies.
    ALL_SIGNIFICANT: exit when all PERMANENT children down.
    Enables cascading supervisor trees.
  end note

  note right of crashrecovery
    **CrashRecovery** — "Let it crash" recovery:
    Isolated virtual thread for retry.
    Exponential backoff with jitter.
    Dead letter queue fallback for failed operations.
    No supervisor restart needed.
  end note

  note right of appcontroller
    **ApplicationController** — App lifecycle:
    Top-level supervisor wrapping entire app.
    start() creates supervisor tree, blocks until ready.
    stop() gracefully shuts down all children.
    Coordinates boot sequence and shutdown.
  end note

  note right of appspec
    **ApplicationSpec** — App configuration:
    Initial supervisor tree structure.
    Boot timeout, initialization function.
    Application state holder (config, resources).
    Passed to ApplicationController.
  end note

  note right of appcallback
    **ApplicationCallback** — App hooks:
    onReady() fires when app fully started.
    onShutdown() fires before shutdown.
    onError(error) for global error handling.
    healthcheck() for k8s liveness probes.
  end note

  note right of starttype
    **StartType** — Sealed enum:
    IMMEDIATE: spawn child now.
    DELAYED: spawn later via dynamicChild.
    DEPENDENT: spawn only after parent ready.
    Enables boot phase coordination.
  end note

  note right of runtype
    **RunType** — Sealed enum:
    FOREGROUND: normal process (counted).
    BACKGROUND: detached (not counted in restarts).
    BOOT_ONLY: shutdown after boot phase.
    Partitions children by lifecycle phase.
  end note

  note on link : Supervisor.create() factory\nSupplier<ChildSpec<S,M>> for dynamic pools
}

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml